<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id78bd27f9-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s831aa"><num value="831aa">§ 831aa.</num><heading> Laws repealed</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">All acts or parts of acts in conflict with this chapter are repealed, so far as they affect the operations contemplated by this chapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id78bd27fa-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/act/1933-05-18/ch32/s28">May 18, 1933, ch. 32, § 28</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/48/71">48 Stat. 71</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
